snippet.description:
"When times were simpler..." Watch the Masters of The Universe teaser for this upcoming live-action adventure movie based on the classic 80’s toy brand. Masters of The Universe stars Nicholas Galitzine, Camila Mendes, Alison Brie, James Purefoy, Morena Baccarin, Jóhannes Haukur Jóhannesson, Charlotte Riley, and Kristin Wiig as the voice of Roboto, with Jared Leto and Idris Elba. The teaser reveals that a full trailer will be released tomorrow, January 22, 2026. Masters of the Universe, directed by Travis Knight, releases on June 5, 2026.
